e_Kate_Kann-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chloe_Moriondo_-_New_Pub_2_-_Madeline_Kate_Kann-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chloe_Moriondo_-_New_Pub_2_-_Madeline_Kate_Kann-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chloe_Moriondo_-_New_Pub_2_-_Madeline_Kate_Kann-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chloe_Moriondo_-_New_Pub_2_-_Madeline_Kate_Kann-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chloe_Moriondo_-_New_Pub_2_-_Madeline_Kate_Kann-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chloe_Moriondo_-_New_Pub_2_-_Madeline_Kate_Kann-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chloe-moriondo">Chloe Moriondo</a>宣布了她的新专辑“ Oyster”的详细信息，并分享了其最新的单曲“ Hate It”  - 在下面查看。</p><p>这位22岁的底特律独立流行音乐家将于3月28日通过公共消费和大西洋唱片发行她的第四张录音室专辑，您可以<a href="https://chloemoriondo.lnk.to/OysterAlbum">在此处</a>预订/预先保存。</p><p>在发行之前，莫里翁多（Moriondo）分享了令人毛骨悚然的单曲“ Hate It”，在其中，她幻想着将陌生人的脸戴在床上或将其滑过头上并抢劫银行。在这里观看曲目的视频： </p><p><iframe title="Chloe Moriondo-讨厌它（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QOzI2E4O3v0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在谈到曲目时，莫里翁多说：“&#39;讨厌它&#39;涵盖了所有嫉妒，仇恨和痴迷的感觉，这些感觉可能会迷上一个无法实现的人，或者渴望过一种无法实现的生活。”</p><p> “我真他妈的狂喜，让这张专辑发行。自从它的概念以来，我一直在渴望发布它，并且我正在爆炸，试图不泄漏所有漏洞。它充满了脆弱性，轻率的暗恋，绝望，聚会和170亿吨盐水。世界是我的牡蛎，很快也将是你的！”</p><p> “ Hate It”是从上一张单曲“ Shoreline”开始的，而专辑是与包括Jonah Summerfield（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/holly-humberstone">Holly Humberstone</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tommy-lefroy">Tommy Lefroy</a> ）和Chloe Kraemer（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-japanese-house">日本房屋</a>）在内的合着者和制片人制作的。</p><h2> <strong>“牡蛎”曲目列表：</strong> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;抓住&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;生的&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“讨厌它”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;深渊&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;牡蛎&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“海岸线”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“寄生虫”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;7海</strong></li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;虚弱的&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;使用&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Roboto" data-listid="965" data-list-defn-props="{" ari